  "local_port": 46340,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How do you pre-select a seat when booking a flight on Royal Air Maroc?",
  "response": "Pre-selecting a seat when booking a flight with Royal Air Maroc can enhance your travel experience by ensuring you have a preferred seat, whether it's by the window, aisle, or with extra legroom. Here\u2019s a step-by-step guide to help you select your seat:\n\n### **1. During Online Booking**\n\n**a. Visit the Official Website:**\n- Go to [Royal Air Maroc's official website](https://www.royalairmaroc.com/).\n\n**b. Start Your Booking:**\n- Enter your flight details (departure and destination cities, travel dates, number of passengers) and proceed to search for available flights.\n\n**c. Select Your Flight:**\n- Choose the flight that best suits your schedule and proceed to the seat selection stage.\n\n**d. Choose Your Seat:**\n- During the booking process, you will reach a seat map where you can view available seats.\n- Click on your preferred seat to select it. Seats may be color-coded based on availability and additional fees (e.g., extra legroom seats might incur an extra cost).\n\n**e. Confirm Selection:**\n- After selecting your seat, continue with the booking process by entering passenger details and payment information.\n\n### **2. After Booking (Manage Booking)**\n\nIf you have already booked your flight and want to select or change your seat:\n\n**a. Access Manage Booking:**\n- Navigate to the [Manage Booking](https://www.royalairmaroc.com/en/manage-booking) section on the Royal Air Maroc website.\n\n**b. Enter Booking Details:**\n- Provide your booking reference number and the last name of the passenger to access your reservation.\n\n**c. Select Seats:**\n- Once your booking details are loaded, look for the option to select or change seats.\n- Choose your preferred seats from the available options. Note that some seats may have additional charges.\n\n**d. Confirm Changes:**\n- After selecting your seats, review any additional fees and confirm the changes.\n\n### **3. Via the Mobile App**\n\nRoyal Air Maroc may offer a mobile app that allows you to manage your booking, including seat selection:\n\n**a. Download the App:**\n- Install the Royal Air Maroc app from the [App Store](https://apps.apple.com/) or [Google Play Store](https://play.google.com/store).\n\n**b. Log In:**\n- Sign in with your booking reference and last name.\n\n**c. Select Seats:**\n- Navigate to the seat selection feature and choose your preferred seats.\n\n### **4. Contacting Customer Service**\n\nIf you encounter difficulties online or prefer assistance:\n\n**a. Call Customer Service:**\n- Reach out to Royal Air Maroc\u2019s customer service via phone. You can find contact numbers on their [Contact Us](https://www.royalairmaroc.com/en/contact-us) page.\n\n**b. Provide Booking Details:**\n- Have your booking reference and personal identification ready to facilitate the process.\n\n**c. Request Seat Selection:**\n- Inform the representative of your seat preferences, and they will assist you in selecting or changing your seat.\n\n### **5. At the Airport**\n\nWhile it's best to select your seat in advance, you can also choose or change your seat during online check-in or at the airport:\n\n**a. Online Check-In:**\n- Typically opens 24 to 48 hours before departure on the Royal Air Maroc website or mobile app. During check-in, you'll have the option to select or change seats.\n\n**b. Airport Check-In Counter:**\n- Visit the Royal Air Maroc check-in counter or self-service kiosks at the airport to select your seat. Availability may be limited, and preferred seats might already be taken.\n\n### **Additional Tips**\n\n- **Fees:** Be aware that certain seats, especially those with extra legroom or in preferred locations, may incur additional charges.\n  \n- **Frequent Flyers:** If you are a member of Royal Air Maroc's loyalty program (Safar Flyer), you may have access to complimentary seat selection or priority for certain seats based on your membership tier.\n\n- **Early Booking:** Seat availability can be limited, so it\u2019s advisable to select your seat as early as possible during the booking process to secure your preferred choice.\n\n- **Check Policies:** Review Royal Air Maroc\u2019s [seat selection policy](https://www.royalairmaroc.com/en/information-service/faq/faq-seat-selection) for any specific guidelines or updates that may affect your ability to choose seats.\n\nBy following these steps, you can efficiently pre-select your seat on Royal Air Maroc flights, ensuring a more comfortable and personalized travel experience.",
